essed, please try again'=>'支付无法处理，请再试一次','Payment detected and confirmed. Customer still need to send'=>'支付已检测并确认。客户仍需发送','Payment error:'=>'支付错误：','Payment method description that the customer will see on your checkout'=>'客户在您的结账页面上将看到的支付方式描述','Please choose a cryptocurrency'=>'请选择一种加密货币','Please renew your subscription'=>'请续订您的订阅','Please renew your subscription on %1$s. You can pay the renewal when you’re ready: %2$s'=>'请在%1$s上续订您的订阅。您可以在准备好时支付续订费用：%2$s。','Please select a Cryptocurrency'=>'请选择一种加密货币','PLEASE SEND'=>'请发送','Processing can take some time depending on the blockchain.'=>'处理时间可能根据区块链的不同而有所不同。','QR Code by default'=>'默认二维码','QR code image size.'=>'二维码图像大小.','QR Code size'=>'二维码大小','QR Code to show'=>'要显示的二维码','QR Code with value'=>'带有金额的二维码','QR Code without value'=>'无金额的二维码','Refresh converted value'=>'刷新转换值','Select how you want to show the QR Code to the user. Either select a default to show first, or hide one of them.'=>'选择您想如何向用户显示二维码。选择一个默认显示，或隐藏其中一个。','Select which coins do you wish to accept. CTRL + click to select multiple. Addresses must be set on the dashboard.'=>'选择您希望接受的硬币。按住CTRL键并单击以选择多个。地址必须在仪表板上设置。






